        <div class="contentBody">
            <h1> Rooms</h1>
            <div  class="centerPageText">
                <p>
                    Here at the Sodus Shores Lodge, we have four different rooms available. Any room is perfect for a weekend 
                    getaway, bachelor/bachelorette parties, fishermen and ice fishermen, snowmobilers, charter captains, we 
                    have had them all.
                </p>
                <h2> All Room Amenities </h2>
                <p>
                    -Queen Bed                         <br>
                    -Twin Bed                          <br>
                    -Cable T.V.                        <br>
                    -Mini Refrigerator                 <br>
                    -Access to Bathrooms with Showers  <br>
                    -Air Conditioning                  <br>
                    -Heat                              <br>
                    -All Bedding is Supplied           <br>
                </p>
                <h2> Pricing </h2>
                <p>
                    IN SEASON (April to September): $125 Per Night, Per Room. <br>
                    OUT OF SEASON (October to March): $100 Per Night, Per Room.
                </p>
                <h3> All Rooms Have a Strict No-Smoking and No Pet Policy </h3>
                <h3> We Also Ask that a Mask is Worn in Common Areas </h3>
                <h3> A deposit of 50% is required for multiple room bookings </h3>
                <h3> Cancellations must be within 48 hours to receive a refund </h3>
            </div>
        <!-- Room 1 -->
            <div class="room">
                <img src="assets/imgs/room1.jpg">
                <h1> Room 1: </h1>
                <p>
                    Room 1 has one queen bed and all the things listed in the amenities. Pictured 
                    here to the right, it is perfect for one or two people staying however long you 
                    need. The bathroom is right down the hall and is located near the front door.
                </p>
            </div>
        <!-- Room 2 -->
            <div class="room">
                <img src="assets/imgs/room2.jpg">
                <h1> Room 2: </h1>
                <p>
                    Room 2 has one queen bed and a single bed with all the listed amenities. Pictured 
                    to the right it can sleep one to three people comfortably. The bathroom is also right 
                    down the hall and is also located near the front door.
                </p>
            </div>
        <!-- Room 3 -->
            <div class="room">
                <img src="assets/imgs/room3.jpg">
                <h1> Room 3: </h1>
                <p>
                    Room 3 along with the other amenities has a queen bed, a single bed, and a sink in the 
                    room. This is the only room with a sink and mirror inside making it easier to wash up 
                    quickly, brush your teeth, or do anything else you would need to all in your own room. 
                    This room is also conveniently located next to the bathroom and is down the hall a little 
                    ways from the front door.
                </p>
            </div>        
        <!-- Room 4 -->
            <div class="room">
                <img src="assets/imgs/room4.jpg">
                <h1> Room 4: </h1>
                <p>
                    Room 4 comes with all the other amenities, a queen bed, and a single bed. Located just 
                    down the hall from the bathroom and furthest from the front door. This room is furthest 
                    from the front door which provides it with a little bit more privacy than the other rooms.
                </p>
            </div>        
